data.description: Nestled on 3 acres, this 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home with a 2-car garage offers the epitome of modern living. The kitchen is a culinary dream, featuring a spacious island, breakfast bar, and a 5-burner gas range stove, complemented by reverse osmosis for pure water and a Culligan water softener for added luxury. Inside, an indoor utility room and drop zone add convenience. The master bedroom boasts a generous walk-in closet, while the master bathroom exudes elegance with its double vanity, soaker tub, and oversized shower. A second bathroom features a marble vanity, and throughout the house, laminate wood design flooring enhances the aesthetic. Outdoors, the 30' x 40' shop/barn with painted flooring and a stall provide storage, while an outdoor kitchen w/ a refrigerator and grill awaits. A pool with a hot tub completes the backyard oasis, all enclosed within a fenced yard with a cross fence for versatility. This property offers a harmonious blend of comfort, style, and outdoor allure.
